Titolo: My Child Lebensborn

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: My Child Lebensborn is a 2018 social simulation game developed by Teknopilot for iOS, Android and Windows. The player takes the role of parenting a lebensborn child in Norway after World War II and helps them to navigate growing up and bullying that they face because of their background. The game received praise for its portrayal of emotional trauma, but reviewers noted that the game could be tough to play through.

Genere: Social simulation game

Valutazione: N/A
